sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM athletes 
WHERE sport = 'Gymnastics';

external_knowledge:
External knowledge used:

- "Crown jewel clubs" refers to the top-performing clubs for each event;
- "Won the most prizes" refers to the clubs with the highest total medals for each event;
- "Treasures" and "accolades" refer to the total number of medals won by the clubs;
- "Conquered" refers to the events in which the clubs have won medals.
